source.name: Street Sweeping - Chart View
source.description: Measures the percentage of Edmonton residential neighbourhoods that have been street sweeped as part of the yearly neighbourhood street sweeping program. As mandated in City Bylaw (###), 100% of residential neighbourhoods are to be swept in the (six?) week period from (date) to (date).
